40MH?  I do 65MH on my 2080Ti.  This whole thing is total crap.  There is nothing wrong with buying a gaming card and wanting to mine a little bit on the side.  Gimping even that is a slap in the face to everyone paying full price for these cards.  This crap should be illegal.  That's like selling me a truck but telling me I can only put groceries in the bed.

Miners are not the problem!  Scalpers are.  Miners do not buy cards and put them on ebay.  Scalper do!  There are plenty of cards for sale on the open market.

None of this garbage will ever stop until they go back to NOT allowing warranty for grey market product.
